Implement Community Wide Energy Challenge:
-It would involve people volunteering to monitor their homes in order to win a prize;
-Maritime Electric bills would be used to monitor each household;
-Final results would be comparing the average energy consumption per person per square foot of living space;
-The competition would occur over one month and could be held on an annual basis.

